<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=7832&amp;p=34777#p34777"><![CDATA[
A way not so much to control specific order but to have points in the Start Menu that are assigned gravity names along with the ability to associated menu items with gravity names. <br /><br />A very useful extension would be to also be able to assign gravity points on the desktop. <br /><br />Wish I had time to learn enough about deep Windows to do this.  Willing to share my ideas, open source style, if asked by an interesting enough person.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=27284">yet-another-sheller</a> — Wed Nov 22, 2017 11:13 am</p><hr />
